  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/fa4d9dbe8c130f7b.jpg?v=1782537092\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Got this silhouette of Jack custom made from Postmark Studios. Love that there are a large variety of colors to choose from. I chose the 5x7 and the color \"Pool\". So excited to have had an Ikea trip planned, where I was able to get this frame and put it in right away.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"10b-Postmark+Studios+Silhouette+of+Jack+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0f099a414fa58a52.jpg?v=1782537095\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"10c-Postmark+Studios+Silhouette+of+Jack+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7755511f88eafafc.jpg?v=1782537098\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10d-Postmark+Studios+Silhouette+of+Jack+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6bca7f163046ec7b.jpg?v=1782537100\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10e-Postmark+Studios+Silhouette+of+Jack+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/fa8825607d927da8.jpg?v=1782537104\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Right now it's in our living room, at least until I figure out whether or not we are redoing the gallery wall in Jack's room. I think it would be fun to have one of these made every year or so!</p>"
